Name: Heavy Rescue: 401
Title: I'm On My Way
Desc: The OPP responds to a tragedy that rocks the community; a load of confetti shreds Mitch's nerves.
LongDescription: The OPP responds to a tragedy that rocks the towing community; when Sonny gets caught on a dangerous stretch of road, he must turn to an unexpected source for help; a truckload of confetti shreds Mitch's nerves.
